#. HTML: <section class="sutta" id="sn46.15"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn46.15:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 46 "
msgstr "Linked Discourses 46 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn46.15:0.2"
msgid "2. Gilānavagga "
msgstr "2. Sick "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn46.15:0.3"
msgid "15. Dutiyagilānasutta "
msgstr "15. Sick (2nd) "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "sn46.15:1.1"
msgid "Ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā rājagahe viharati veḷuvane kalandakanivāpe. "
msgstr "At one time the Buddha was staying near Rājagaha, in the Bamboo Grove, the squirrels’ feeding ground. "

msgctxt "sn46.15:1.2"
msgid "Tena kho pana samayena āyasmā mahāmoggallāno gijjhakūṭe pabbate viharati ābādhiko dukkhito bāḷhagilāno. "
msgstr "Now at that time Venerable Mahāmoggallāna was staying on the Vulture’s Peak mountain, and he was sick, suffering, gravely ill. "

msgctxt "sn46.15:1.3"
msgid "Atha kho bhagavā sāyanhasamayaṃ paṭisallānā vuṭṭhito yenāyasmā mahāmoggallāno tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā paññatte āsane nisīdi. Nisajja kho bhagavā āyasmantaṃ mahāmoggallānaṃ etadavoca: "
msgstr "Then in the late afternoon, the Buddha came out of retreat, went to Venerable Moggallāna, sat down on the seat spread out, and said to him: "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc2
msgctxt "sn46.15:2.1"
msgid "“Kacci te, moggallāna, khamanīyaṃ kacci yāpanīyaṃ? Kacci dukkhā vedanā paṭikkamanti, no abhikkamanti; paṭikkamosānaṃ paññāyati, no abhikkamo”ti? "
msgstr "“Moggallāna, I hope you’re keeping well; I hope you’re alright. And I hope the pain is fading, not growing, that its fading is evident, not its growing.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn46.15:2.2"
msgid "“Na me, bhante, khamanīyaṃ, na yāpanīyaṃ. Bāḷhā me dukkhā vedanā abhikkamanti, no paṭikkamanti; abhikkamosānaṃ paññāyati, no paṭikkamo”ti. "
msgstr "“Sir, I’m not keeping well, I’m not alright. The pain is terrible and growing, not fading; its growing is evident, not its fading.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc3
msgctxt "sn46.15:3.1"
msgid "“Sattime, moggallāna, bojjhaṅgā mayā sammadakkhātā bhāvitā bahulīkatā abhiññāya sambodhāya nibbānāya saṃvattanti. "
msgstr "“Moggallāna, I’ve rightly explained these seven awakening factors. When developed and cultivated, they lead to direct knowledge, to awakening, and to extinguishment. "

msgctxt "sn46.15:3.2"
msgid "Katame satta? "
msgstr "What seven? "

msgctxt "sn46.15:3.3"
msgid "Satisambojjhaṅgo kho, moggallāna, mayā sammadakkhāto bhāvito bahulīkato abhiññāya sambodhāya nibbānāya saṃvattati … pe … upekkhāsambojjhaṅgo kho, moggallāna, mayā sammadakkhāto bhāvito bahulīkato abhiññāya sambodhāya nibbānāya saṃvattati. "
msgstr "The awakening factors of mindfulness, investigation of principles, energy, rapture, tranquility, immersion, and equanimity. "

msgctxt "sn46.15:3.4"
msgid "Ime kho, moggallāna, satta bojjhaṅgā mayā sammadakkhātā bhāvitā bahulīkatā abhiññāya sambodhāya nibbānāya saṃvattantī”ti. "
msgstr "These are the seven awakening factors that I’ve rightly explained. When developed and cultivated, they lead to direct knowledge, to awakening, and to extinguishment.” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "sn46.15:3.5"
msgid "“Taggha, bhagavā, bojjhaṅgā; "
msgstr "“Indeed, Blessed One, these are awakening factors! "

msgctxt "sn46.15:3.6"
msgid "taggha, sugata, bojjhaṅgā”ti. "
msgstr "Indeed, Holy One, these are awakening factors!” "

#. HTML: </p><p>
#. REF: sc4
msgctxt "sn46.15:4.1"
msgid "Idamavoca bhagavā. "
msgstr "That is what the Buddha said. "

msgctxt "sn46.15:4.2"
msgid "Attamano āyasmā mahāmoggallāno bhagavato bhāsitaṃ abhinandi. "
msgstr "Satisfied, Venerable Mahāmoggallāna was happy with what the Buddha said. "

msgctxt "sn46.15:4.3"
msgid "Vuṭṭhahi cāyasmā mahāmoggallāno tamhā ābādhā. "
msgstr "And that’s how he recovered from that illness. "

msgctxt "sn46.15:4.4"
msgid "Tathāpahīno cāyasmato mahāmoggallānassa so ābādho ahosīti. "
msgstr " "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn46.15:4.5"
msgid "Pañcamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

